For the purposes of this Regulation, the Council, the Commission service listed in Annex II to this Regulation and the High Representative are designated as 'controller' within the meaning of point (8) of Article 3 of Regulation (EU) 2018/1725 of the European Parliament amd of the Council

Regulation (EU) 2018/1725 of the European Parliament and the Council of 23 October 2018 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data by the Union institutions, bodies, offices and agencies and on the free movement of such data, and repealing Regulation (EC) No 45/2001 and Decision No 1247/2002/EC (OJ L 295, 21.11.2018, p. 39).';
                                                , in order to ensure that the natural persons concerned can exercise their rights under that Regulation.
